author: The Associated Press
title: 3 dead in Clark County home after domestic argument
text:
VANCOUVER, Wash. — Officials in Clark County say a couple in their 40s and the woman’s 66-year-old mother are dead after a shooting in the Hazel Dell home .
The sheriff’s office says the shooting occurred Tuesday evening after a domestic argument.
Robert Gutierrez and Elizabeth Orozco were killed along with her mother, Adela Ruiz-Gonzales, who was visiting from Mexico.
Three children ranging in age from 11 to 19 were in the home at the time of the shooting, but were not hurt. They’ve been taken to an undisclosed location.
 The sheriff’s office says no additional suspects are being sought and there is no danger to the community.
The Associated Press
